  <description>
    <p>
    Linthesia is a game. A game of playing music! You only need a MIDI file to play, and a MIDI keyboard (or your PC keyboard).
    </p>
    <p lang="es">Linthesia es un juego. Un juego para tocar música! Solo necesitas un fichero MIDI para tocar, y un teclado MIDI (o tu teclado de PC)</p>
    <p lang="en_GB">Linthesia is a game. A game of playing music! You only need a MIDI file to play, and a MIDI keyboard (or your PC keyboard).</p>
    <p>
    It's a fork of Synthesia, which only runs on Windows and OS X. Linthesia is for GNU/Linux.
    </p>
    <p lang="es">Es un fork de Synthesia, que solo funciona en Window y OS X. Linthesia es para GNU/Linux</p>
